arStrings.szText: While {c_important}{u}Unstoppable{/u}{/c} and for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds after, you gain {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%+|]{/c} increased Movement Speed and can move freely through enemies.
{c_important}{u}Unstoppable{/u}{/c} grants {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%+|]{/c} Movement Speed and the ability to move freely through enemies.
